ts.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Lil+Pump|title=Discography Lil Pump|website=charts.nz|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\" | [[Sverigetopplistan|SWE]]<br /><ref name=\"SWE\">{{cite web|url=http://www.swedishcharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Lil+Pump|title=Discography Lil Pump|website=swedishcharts.com|accessdate=April 20, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Lil Pump (album)|Lil Pump]]''\n|\n* Released: October 6, 2017\n* Label: Tha Lights Global, [[Warner Bros. Records|Warner Bros.]]\n* Format: [[Compact Disc|CD]], [[LP record|LP]], [[Compact Cassette|cassette]], [[Music download|Digital download]], [[Streaming media|Streaming]]\n| 3 || 2 || 80 || 6 || 10 || 52 || 19 || 46 || 20 || 33\n|\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]]: Gold<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&ar=lil+pump&ti=&lab=&genre=&format=Album&date_option=release&from=&to=&award=&type=&category=&adv=SEARCH#search_section |title=American album ceritifications: Lil Pump \u2013 Lil Pump |publisher=[[Recording Industry Association of America]] |date=June 21, 2018 |accessdate=September 8, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Harverd Dropout]]''\n|\n* Released: February 22, 2019<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bloom |first1=Madison |last2=Minsker |first2=Evan |title=Lil Pump's New Album Harverd Dropout Gets Release Date |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/lil-pumps-new-album-harverd-dropout-gets-release-date/ |website=[[Pitchfork (website)|Pitchfork]] |accessdate=January 24, 2019 |date=January 24, 2019}}</ref>\n* Label: Tha Lights Global, Warner Bros.\n* Format: CD, LP, Digital download, Streaming\n| 7 || 3 || 36 || 7 || 19|| 46 || 55 || 21 || \u2014 || 35\n|\n* RIAA: Gold<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.riaa.com/gold-platinum/?tab_active=default-award&ar=lil+pump&ti=&lab=&genre=&format=Album&date_option=release&from=&to=&award=&type=&category=&adv=SEARCH#search_section |title=American album ceritificati