ater\"\n| rowspan=\"9\"| 2016\n| iON\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Johnny\"\n| [[Smokepurpp]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Wristwork\"\n| Richy Samo\n| ''The American Psycho EP''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Where's the Blow\"\n| [[Ski Mask the Slump God]]\n| ''Drown-In-Designer''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"PistolGripPapi\"\n| Lil Sega\n| rowspan=\"12\" data-sort-value=\"\" style=\"background: #ececec; color: #2C2C2C; vertical-align: middle; font-size: smaller; text-align: center; \" class=\"table-na\" | Non-album track\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Count\"\n| Lil Ominous, Smokepurpp\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bitch!\"\n| Lil Ominous\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Bullshit (Kickstand)\"\n| BrentRambo, Warhol.ss, Smokepurpp\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Whippin'\"\n| Stepdadfla, [[Famous Dex]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Trixxx\"\n| rowspan=\"9\"| 2017\n| [[Ronny J]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Two Guns\"\n| Famous Dex, Smokepurpp\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Big Bank\"\n| iON\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Magic\"\n| Richy Samo\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"OK\"\n| Smokepurpp\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Gucci Breakfast\"\n| Smokepurpp\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"M.O.B.\"\n| Splash Zanotti, [[Riff Raff (rapper)|Riff Raff]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"DestGang\"\n| DestoDubb, Richy Samo\n| ''Thank You Fizzle''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Walked In Ready\"\n| JBan$, [[Lil Yachty]]\n| ''JBAN$2TURNT''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Trap Jumpin'\"\n| rowspan=\"11\"| 2018\n| [[Juicy J]]\n| ''Shutdafukup''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Designer (On My Drip)\"\n| Dom Chasin Paper\n| rowspan=\"2\" data-sort-value=\"\" style=\"background: #ececec; color: #2C2C2C; vertical-align: middle; font-size: smaller; text-align: center; \" class=\"table-na\" | Non-album track\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lie Detector\"\n| 24hrs\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Baby Daddy\"\n| [[Lil Yachty]], [[Offset (rapper)|Offset]]\n| ''[[Lil Boat 2]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Face Tats\"\n| DestoDubb\n| ''Thank You Fizzle''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Choppa 4\"\n| Remember SJT\n| rowspan=\"1\" data-sort-value=\